# No API key needed — model calls use your Claude Pro/Max subscription via the
# Claude Code login on this machine (run `claude`, then `/login`, once).
# Optional: a long-lived subscription token from `claude setup-token`, for
# headless machines where the interactive login isn't available.
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=

# Optional: compiler override (defaults to g++)
# CXX=clang++
